>> time required: 2 hours
>> course: main

In pot combine @chicken broth{1%liter}, @soy sauce{3%tbsp}, @garlic cloves{3}, @ginger{2%tbsp}, and @sugar{1%tsp}
Bring to boil and add @chicken thighs{500%g}, reduce heat and simmer ~{40%minutes}
Take @cellophane noodles{250%g} in bowl and cover with warm water. 
When chicken is done remove, cool and shred. Remove any grease from broth and return chicken. 
Stir noodles in broth and simmer for 5 minutes, until noodles are soft. 
Garnish with green onions. 